records.title: Realisation that I'm lost
records.entry: Finally, I have a bit more clarity towards myself now. Seemingly, being bad with directions and having mid life crisis shares a similar causation. That which is the failure to find oneself. And if I shall be unable to find myself, it is no wonder I am not capable to find my other half. I shall divert my efforts into finding myself in hopes that one day someone will be able to find me.
